description.narrative: The objective of the Project is to support the functioning of AD MEPSO in the context of the regional power market through financing investments necessary to rehabilitate and upgrade the power transmission network, increase the level of interconnection with neighboring power systems, and to strengthen the institutional capacity of AD MEPSO.
